        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 45,
        "end": 50
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_022_000159",
    "sentence": "庶人友珪僭位，授鄧州宣化軍節度使、檢校太尉、兼侍中。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "授鄧州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 7,
        "end": 10
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_022_000160",
    "sentence": "末帝即位，移授許州匡國軍節度使，加檢校太師。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "移授許州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 5,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_022_000161",
    "sentence": "五年，蔡州刺史王彥溫作亂，檀受詔討平之，加兼中書令。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "五年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      },
      {
        "text": "蔡州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 3,
        "end": 5
      },
      {
        "text": "刺史",
